  <article class="prose">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I'm Çagri Çimen. I lead engineering teams and spend most of my days working alongside AI
      coding tools — Claude Code, Cursor, MCP servers, and whatever else is useful that week. I
      like shipping things with small teams and writing down what I learn so I don't have to
      re-learn it.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is my working notebook. It holds essays, short notes, guides, and projects,
      loosely organised by topic. Nothing here is finished — most of it will get revised as I
      learn more. That's the point.
    </p>
  </article>
